Package org.jbei.ice.lib.parsers

Parsers for different file formats.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDNAParser
    An object that parser sequences and generates an annotated DNASequence object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ABIParser
    Parse ABI sequence trace file by wrapping BioJava.
    AbstractParser
    This class provides skeletal implementation of IDNAParser interface.
    GeneralParser
    Helper class to set up a list of parsers to iterate over, to try to parse the input file.
    PlainParser
    Parser to handle file with simply nucleotide sequences.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidFormatParserException
    Exception class for parsers.
